{
  "stem": "20848.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It tastes exactly like spinach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And also we were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We couldn't get any other meat except horse meat, and that not very often.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we started buying horse meat and eating horse meat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my father always used to joke, he used to walk in the middle of street pretending he is a horse.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, this is all childish, because things were starting to get grimmer and grimmer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in-- I remember that I had a, a lot of friends there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And in that Rgrodewa 29, we had an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the orphanage was created right during the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I think it was created already for children who were orphaned during the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Their parents were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this orphanage was, took a whole floor in this big house that we lived, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the people who live in the house, they looked after the orphanage, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They used to play cards and take money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They used to make all different kind of evenings and make money to support this orphanage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I remember that we children, we used to do the same.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We used to make pantomime and sell tickets for you know, for very little money and bring money to this orphanage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they started to grab people like-- I remember when things started to get very grim.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I remember that I heard-- we heard in-- in Warsaw that the president of the Warsaw Committee-- Adam Czerniakow was his name-- committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "What happened was apparently the Germans went up to him and wanted him to sign a document to say that he allows-- which is ridiculous-- that he allows the Germans to take the Jews wherever they want to take them.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
